<div class="flex flex-col">
    <!-- Intro text -->
    <h1 class="text-4xl text-center">Stuff I've made</h1>
    <p class="text-md text-center pt-1 max-w-prose mx-auto">Different projects and applications that I've made. Includes both scientific and non-scientific projects. Some are less complete.</p>

